  "remarks": "The Industrial Development and Renovation Organisation is a government body responsible for acceleration of Iran’s industrialisation. It is involved in the nuclear and missile programmes and provides support to the Iranian industrial sector. Therefore, the Industrial Development and Renovation Organisation is owned or controlled by and supports the Government of Iran.",
